data.description: Welcome to your dream home! This stunning listing offers the perfect blend of comfort, style, and functionality. Nestled in a serene neighborhood, this spacious 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom home is designed with a modern open concept and features a split master floorplan that maximizes privacy and convenience. Upon entering you'll be greeted by a warm and inviting atmosphere. The open concept layout seamlessly connects the living room, dining area, and kitchen, creating an expansive and airy living space. Natural light pours in through large windows illuminating every corner and creating a bright and cheerful ambiance. The heart of the home is the well-appointed kitchen which boasts sleek countertops, ample cabinetry, and stainless steel appliances. Whether you're a seasoned chef or enjoy casual cooking this kitchen offers the perfect setting for culinary creativity. The adjacent dining area provides a lovely space for gathering with loved ones and enjoying delicious meals together. The generous master suite offers a private retreat for relaxation and rejuvenation. It includes a spacious bedroom, a walk-in closet, and a luxurious en-suite bathroom complete with double vanities, a jetted soaking tub, and a separate shower. The two additional bedrooms are thoughtfully positioned on the opposite side of the home, providing a peaceful haven for family members or guests. These rooms offer ample space, natural light, and easy access to the second full bathroom, ensuring everyone's comfort and convenience. Stepping outside, you'll discover a backyard oasis perfect for outdoor entertaining or peaceful moments of tranquility. Whether you're hosting a barbecue, gardening, or simply enjoying the fresh air, this well-maintained outdoor space provides endless possibilities. Don't miss the opportunity to make this 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom home with an open concept split master floorplan your own. Schedule a viewing today and prepare to be captivated by its charm and elegance.
